name.en: All-out Defense Education Military Training - Civil Defense
name.ch: 全民國防教育軍事訓練-全民國防

notice.ch: 曾修過同一科課程、外籍生(含陸生)不得選修本門課程

remark.ch: 曾修過同一科課程、外籍生(含陸生)不得選修本門課程

goal.ch:
1.認識國防政策，建立國家安全概念。
2.深化全民國防共識，凝聚憂患意識。
3.熟悉安全應變機制，堅定防衛國家意識。
goal.en:
1. Understand national defense policy and establish the concept of national security.
2. Deepen the national defense consensus and gather the sense of crisis.
3. Familiar with the security response mechanism and strengthen the national awareness of defense.

outline.ch: 國家意識、全民防衛、國防與經濟、文化與心理及其他相關課程。
outline.en: National awareness, national defense, national defense and economy, culture and psychology and other related courses.

instructMethod.ch:
講授
研討

個別指導

gradMethod.ch: 出席率30％、平時成績10％、期中報告30％、期末考30％
gradMethod.en: Attendance rate 30％, usual grades 10％, midterm report 30％, final exam 30％
